condition.narrative: Accounts receivable not to exceed 3 months billings by October 1, 2007 and onwards
JIRAMA will prepare quarterly mgmt rpts satisfactory to IDA (incl. relevant tech, commercial, & financial data) & submit said rptto IDA no later than 60 days after end of each quarter
No disbursement under Category 1 (a) unless the Recipient has submitted a report satisfactory to IDA on the condition of theVatomandry dam and the proposed safety measures to be implemented
No disbursement under category 1 (c) unless Recipient has recruited a technical advisor w/qualifications and experiencesatisfactory to IDA
No later than April 1, 2013, the Recipient shall have publicly disclosed the Electricity tariff Indexation Formula and adjustedelectricity tariffs in accordance with said formula
No later than November 30, 2006, the Recipient shall have adopted the Electricity tariff Indexation Formula
Recip. to define, in agree. w/IDA, no later than Sept 30 each yr during proj. implementation, amounts to be injected byBeneficiary, into JIRAMA during following calendar yr so as to allow normal OPs
Recipient shall have established terms and conditions to be used in the contracting of JIRAMA's private partner satisfactory totheAssociation and have launched the prequalification process
Recipient shall have launched the bidding process for the recruitment of a new private operator for the management of JIRAMA'soperations.
Recipient shall have publicly disclosed Elec Tariff Indexation Formula & adjusted elec tariffs in accord. w/said formula, & shallsubsequently adjust said tariffs in accord. w/said formula every 6 mos
